even without the endometriosis.

628
00:51:55.900 --> 00:51:58.371
So if you get surgery and treatments for a year,

629
00:51:58.371 --> 00:52:00.101
it may become more difficult than it is now.

630
00:52:02.601 --> 00:52:05.371
It's not like she can never have kids, right?

631
00:52:06.740 --> 00:52:09.411
It would be nice to get a fertility treatment now, but...

632
00:52:10.780 --> 00:52:12.450
It isn't impossible.

633
00:52:53.351 --> 00:52:54.490
I...

634
00:52:55.521 --> 00:52:57.121
made you get your hopes up.

635
00:52:58.990 --> 00:53:01.231
