636
00:53:02.161 --> 00:53:03.300
please don't.

637
00:53:06.001 --> 00:53:08.441
Do you remember what I said?

638
00:53:11.211 --> 00:53:12.970
I told you to focus on yourself...

639
00:53:14.180 --> 00:53:16.041
