640
00:53:20.150 --> 00:53:21.521
What's the matter?

641
00:53:35.130 --> 00:53:36.501
The test results weren't that good.

642
00:53:42.271 --> 00:53:43.641
I could get treated for another three months...

643
00:53:44.941 --> 00:53:47.271
and repeat the same thing all over again.

644
00:53:48.081 --> 00:53:49.311
But I can't guarantee...

645
00:53:51.650 --> 00:53:52.880
that the result will come out okay.

646
00:54:01.161 --> 00:54:02.661
If you're enduring your pain...

647
00:54:07.800 --> 00:54:11.731
because you want to wait until I'm ready,

648
00:54:11.831 --> 00:54:12.970
just don't.

649
00:54:15.601 --> 00:54:16.771
I've been...

650
00:54:17.340 --> 00:54:20.070
postponing it because it'll make things harder for me.

651
00:54:22.541 --> 00:54:24.550
It's not because of you.

652
00:54:28.950 --> 00:54:30.320
There's still a chance...

653
00:54:30.921 --> 00:54:33.791
for you to get pregnant even after the surgery.

654
00:54:35.021 --> 00:54:38.061
You can look for a way once you're better.

655
00:54:39.760 --> 00:54:43.200
But now, you need to get the surgery.

656
00:54:47.430 --> 00:54:48.800
Are you okay?

657
00:54:51.570 --> 00:54:53.240
I'm sure you're having a hard time as well.

658
00:54:58.880 --> 00:55:00.481
I'm okay.

659
00:55:15.061 --> 00:55:16.061
What's wrong?

660
00:55:17.671 --> 00:55:19.470
Is it because of Ha Ri's illness?

661
00:55:20.271 --> 00:55:23.001
Are you thinking of postponing the wedding?

662
00:55:23.641 --> 00:55:26.311
No, not at all.

663
00:55:29.141 --> 00:55:30.481
Ha Ri might...

664
00:55:31.880 --> 00:55:33.711
